# Wishlist Price Tracker App

A smart wishlist app to track product prices on **Amazon** and **Flipkart**. Users can add product links, set target prices, and get notified when the price drops.  
This project includes a **SwiftUI iOS frontend** and a **Node.js backend**.

---

## Project Structure
wishlist-project/
├── wishlist/        # SwiftUI frontend
├── node/            # Node.js backend
└── README.md
---

## Features

- Add Amazon/Flipkart product links.
- Fetch product details (title, current price, image).
- Set target price alerts.
- Monitor price changes automatically.
- Real-time updates with Firebase Firestore (optional).

---

## Requirements

- **iOS frontend**: Xcode 15+, SwiftUI  
- **Backend**: Node.js 18+, npm  
- **Database**: Firebase Firestore (optional for real-time price tracking)  
- **Network**: iPhone and computer on same Wi-Fi (for local testing)

---

